 have gotten used to, is the ability to use the Mouse Wheel, as haing to use the 1-6 keys on my keyboard have more than once caused me to use a potion when I wanted to use my magic wand.This game is FREAKING AWESOME, if you were ever in the times of floppy disks, and played those old dungeon crawlers, and love rouge-likes, and having to fear for your life because there is perma-death in the game, this game is your new best friend!I have a couple of videos so far on the game and making a Let's Play on the game!https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j5-wPdHgBWkhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=COnzuENBzds"
